Description:
Exceptional Class and Facilities in Marina Tower
Showcasing a unique floorplan that allows for both open and private living in the dazzling Marina Tower, this brand new and utterly sophisticated 2 bedroom + study, 2 bathroom Docklands oasis is sure to take your breath away.
This immaculate apartment shows off with bright floor-to-ceiling windows, premium carpet, quality stone, and an array of other superior fittings and fixtures throughout. The layout of this residence is truly amazing, with both bedrooms on either side of the generous central lounge and dining zone allowing for that extra bit of privacy at night.
The designer kitchen has an island bench, ample storage, and Miele appliances, while the master bedroom just off the kitchen enjoys a built-in robe and pristine ensuite as well as scenic park views. The other bedroom also boasts park views as well as access to a dedicated study, while further embrace the stylish main bathroom, large covered balcony terrace with views, European laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, secure intercom, and car space.
Take advantage of the brilliant Marina Tower facilities which include an opulent lobby lounge, library, private business centre, meeting rooms, cinema, lounge and billiard room, kitchen and dining area, rooftop pool, gym, and expansive deck. You’re also near Harbour Town Shopping Centre, Ron Barassi Snr Park, local restaurants and bars, Moonee Ponds Creek Trail, and the 30, 75, and 86 trams.
Please contact Charles Finnigan on 0437 204 556 to arrange an exclusive viewing

Description:
YARRA'S EDGE GEM
Presentation perfect with unrivalled 270 degree panoramic views from the bay across the bridges to the Yarra and the city skyline, this impressive three-bedroom apartment with two bathrooms on the 12th floor is the epitome of inner city living. Capturing glorious northern sun, this immaculate home enjoys open plan entertaining with a huge balcony terrace which is one of the largest in the building. Also includes designer Smeg appliances kitchen / meals, hotel style main bedroom (BIRs & ensuite) & a wing of 3 bedrooms (BIRs) with extra built in cabinetry and new sheer and block out blinds including newly fitted curtains in all bedrooms. The apartment also includes stone bench tops, zoned heating / cooling, video intercom & two security U/C car spaces, a storage cage and floorboards throughout. It's pure excellence complete with lift access, and use of the pool, gym & BBQ facilities. The apartment plan is one that rarely becomes available is the other bonus is that its available to own and occupy straight away.
The facilities include access to Mirvac’s Rekdek which contains an indoor heated lap pool, spa, steam and sauna room, and fully equipped gymnasium.
For inspections please call Glenn Donnelly on 0419 998 235

Description:
Townhouse Brilliance with a Location to Cherish
With a remarkable position, this sophisticated and utterly stylish 3 bedroom + study, 2.5 bathroom residence is a class above the others.
Brilliant location aside, this gorgeous property truly sets the benchmark for townhouse living in the Docklands thanks to its superior quality and amazing attention to detail. A lower ground floor offers a private study as well as your very own garden area perfect for unwinding after a long day at work. Up a few stairs and you enter the light-filled and expansive central living zone, which has designated areas for both dining and a lounge fitted with a charming gas fireplace.
This main hub has a luxury stone kitchen right in the middle of the action, with an island bench perfect for quick meals and premium stainless steel appliances ideal for those who love to cook at home. This level also feeds out to a balcony which delivers views of the Melbourne Star Observation Wheel which is best enjoyed at night.
Three bedrooms dominate the top floor including the master bedroom which comes with a walk-in robe, generous double vanity ensuite, and a balcony. There is also a 2nd study area off one of the other bedrooms and a sleek main bathroom on the top floor. Other property extras include a powder room, laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, storage cage, and 2 secure car spaces.
You’ll love being so close to The District Docklands with brilliant eating choices, retail outlets, and entertainment. You’re also close to IGA X-Press and Asian grocery store, waterside restaurants, Moonee Ponds Creek Trail, and the 30, 75, and 86 trams.
Please contact Charles Finnigan on 0437 204 556 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
AMAZING OPPORTUNITY IN DOCKLANDS
Whether you are a first home buyer or an astute investor, don’t miss out on this incredible chance to buy in the Docklands. Located on La Trobe Street where Docklands meets the CBD sits the Lacrosse Building, ideally located next to Etihad Stadium, public transport, restaurants and shopping.
This 2 bed, 2 bath, apartment, which has fantastic views of the Etihad Stadium, includes a modern kitchen with stone bench tops and dishwasher, mirrored built in robes in the bedrooms, and clean, contemporary finishes in the bathrooms. A Euro-laundry and private balcony round out this well designed apartment.
Completing this apartment is split system heating/cooling, secure swipe/intercom entry, and a secure car space, as well as use of the outdoor pool and gym. Whether you’re enjoying eating out with friends, swimming, shopping, or attending sporting events at Etihad Stadium, this is low maintenance living without the price tag.

SUPERB VALUE IN SENSATIONAL LOCATION
A superb and affordable opportunity with exceptional views awaits you at Lacrosse, where Docklands meets the CBD. Perfect for an astute investor and currently returning approximately 6%, this must see apartment is ideally located next to Etihad Stadium and public transport, with an array of restaurants and retail outlets close by.
Comprised of an open-plan kitchen/living area, this 2 bed, 2 bath, 1 car apartment has fantastic views of the CBD. The modern kitchen comes with stone bench tops, Blanco dishwasher, and concealed fridge, mirrored built in robes in the bedrooms, and clean, contemporary finishes in the bathrooms. A Euro-laundry and private balcony round out this well designed apartment.
Completing this fantastic package is a secure car-park, split system heating & cooling, secure swipe & intercom entry, and use of the residents' pool and gym - everything you could want from inner city living. With public transport, world class shopping, and an array of waterside restaurants and bars on your doorstep, this well laid out pad is perfectly situated only minutes from the CBD and Southern Cross Station.

Description:
DESIGNER STYLE HOME IN HEART OF DOCKLANDS!
Perfectly positioned on level 12 is this spacious two bedroom two bathroom apartment in a highly desirable corner position situated in Docklands' renowned “Watergate” complex. Presented immaculately, this bright and spacious apartment with a total of 108 sqm of space offers 270 degree views including tranquil views overlooking the park and towards the bay.
Immaculately presented, this light-filled, stylish and generously proportioned apartment offers brilliant city, park and harbour views, an elegant balcony, a fresh and modern kitchen with marble stone bench tops, quality stainless steel appliances and a breakfast bar. Zoned separately are two spacious bedrooms and two bathrooms, including the main bedroom’s beautiful en-suite – offering unforgettable luxury.
Features of this large home include:
- Approximately 108sqm of living and terrace space.
- Spacious open plan living area surrounded by double glazed floor to ceiling windows for maximum natural lighting and expansive views
- A wonderfully defined dining area, plus stylish kitchen with marble stone bench tops, quality stainless steel appliances, and breakfast bar,
- Two spacious bedrooms, lavish master bedroom with a study nook and a full ensuite,
- 14sqm undercover balcony
- two secure undercover individual car parks.
- One storage cage
- Secured intercom access
Recreational facilities within the Watergate building include a full size swimming pool, Jacuzzi, gym, sauna, function rooms and communal lawn area for residents, with a multi-purpose sports area located just outside the complex.
This is a great opportunity for owner occupiers and investors alike! Location is perfect; with a tram stop being just downstairs, 500 meters from Southern Cross Station, cafes, restaurants and major shopping precincts within a stone's throw.
Don't miss this great opportunity! Please call Peter Doan on 0423 399 999 to arrange an inspection.

Description:
Picturesque River Views You’ll Love 24/7
With a wonderful north-facing location right on the marina where you’re overlooking the tranquil Yarra River and CBD, this smart and stylish one bedroom apartment is the perfect Docklands opportunity.
Just metres from the lively South Wharf and in the fabulous Yarra’s Edge precinct, this 5th floor apartment has many highlights. Open plan living and meals is a delight for everyday relaxing, while the tiled kitchen is very flexible with a moveable island bench plus stainless steel Miele appliances.
The undercover balcony features the breathtaking river views, with this alfresco area accessed from both the central living zone and bedroom with BIR. Enjoy this amazing location just steps to South Wharf eateries and bars including Charlie Lovett, Common Man, Melbourne Public, and Gasolina. You’re also near IGA X-Press, Capital City Trail, and DFO shopping.

Description:
IMMACULATE SKY HOME
This immaculate sky-high apartment, in one of Docklands most striking towers, offers an escape from it all, up in the clouds.
The Mirvac T5 sits on the banks of the Yarra, across from ANZ’s headquarters and just as short walk from the unique Webb Bridge.
Pass through the stylishly minimal foyer and shoot upwards to the 30th floor, and it doesn’t take long to realize this property is something special. As you step over the threshold the wide, open-plan living space is revealed a rarity in such a modern apartment.
A palette of pale colour, from the luxurious carpets to the tall walls, creates the perfect blank canvas for any avid art collector to leave their mark.
There’s a wall of floor-to-ceiling windows and a sliding door accessing an expansive balcony, ensuring the property is flooded with natural light as the clouds roll by.
The galley-style kitchen sits to one side, with no shortage of stone bench tops to prepare a feast. Stainless steel Miele appliances are set among the cabinetry, adding to the effortless panache evident wherever you look.
The balcony itself is a real treat, turn left and you look down the spine of the Yarra out towards the Bolte Bridge standing proud in the distance and the observation wheel almost directly ahead.
Turn right and the entire city is laid out before you in a breathtaking panorama, with the Rialto and Eureka building standing sentinel. Far below, the boats moored at the marina look like a child’s toy. Spectacular would be an understatement.
The main bedroom demonstrates a dab hand with unique design flair. As you enter, a spacious walk-in wardrobe is tucked away just behind you.
An immaculate ensuite on the right is well-appointed and enveloped tiles. A deep spa-style bath sits before a huge glass wall, cleverly allowing you to gaze out towards the city while you soak away the cares of the worlds. More modest bathers may choose to roll down the blind.
On the other side of the property is a second bedroom with built-in mirrored wardrobes. You can lie in bed and see right out to the Dandenong’s.
Lucky residents can also take full advantage on the RekDek gym, heated lap pool, sauna and steam room. Throw two secure car spaces and a storage cage into the mix and you really are spoiled. It’s all about living the high life.
For a private inspection call Glenn Donnelly on 0419 998 235.

Description:
RARE TWO BEDROOM APARTMENT WITH DUAL ASPECT
This luxurious two bedroom unique floor plan apartment includes the added bonus of a study/guest bedroom and is located on the 20th level of the popular 'Victoria Point' residential complex in the ever-vibrant Victoria Harbour precinct of Docklands. This unique apartment is designed to capture the most amazing views of the Docklands waterfront, the iconic Bolte and Westgate bridges, the bay, city skyline and beyond.
The designer kitchen features stainless steel appliances, stone bench tops and ample cupboard space whilst the spacious dining area adjoins the perfect open plan living room opening onto a wide balcony, perfect for entertaining or taking in the uninterrupted views.
The main bedroom comprises of a chic ensuite bathroom, built-in-robes and a private balcony with magical views of the city. The spacious second bedroom is serviced by the lavish main bathroom with the added extravagance of a bathtub.
Other features of this sensational apartment include a study which can also double as a guest bedroom, a separate laundry, two secure undercover car spaces, ducted air conditioning and heating along with the use of the Gymnasium and Concierge.

Description:
The Arcade with super high ceilings!
Here is a ultra-modern apartment has all the hallmarks of quality living. With a genuine sense of view-filled space and light, the layout is both distinctive and functional with living and dining incorporating a fully equipped galley kitchen, European laundry, two double bedrooms with built-in robes sitting on either side of a designer bathroom highlighted with floor-to-ceiling feature tile. A funky covered balcony facilitates outdoor relaxation and entertaining in sunshine and rain while beamed ceilings above the living room add a hint of warehouse style. Docklands' renowned restaurants, bars, transport options and the mix of specialty and discount retailers at Harbour Town shopping are all on the doorstep.
The apartment also comes with a separate study and a storage cage.
For inspection call Glenn Donnelly on 0419 998 235.

Description:
Picturesque Waters Views and Harbour Lifestyle
From the spacious and smart floorplan to the memorable northerly views of the harbour, this exceptional two bedroom, two bathroom apartment in the ‘Dock 5’ complex is one of the modern treasures of the lively Victoria Harbour precinct.
If you’re ever going to make the Docklands switch then now is the time. This impressive 7th floor retreat is splashed with luxury and quality, with the ever present harbour views a constant highlight whether you’re enjoying them from the north-facing and sizeable living and dining zone or the charming balcony.
The stylish kitchen has the advantage of premium stainless steel appliances including an integrated dishwasher, while the master bedroom benefits from the floor to ceiling water views along with walk-through robes and a dazzling ensuite. Further enjoy a 2nd bedroom with BIR and balcony access, main bathroom with European laundry, ducted heating and cooling, intercom entry, storage cage and secure car space. The property also sits on a large 130 sqm (approx.).
Dock 5 also offers residents a personal wine cellar plus access to a swimming pool, gym, library, BBQ area and concierge. The Victoria Harbour precinct is a collection of retail and office spaces, where you’re close to Library at The Dock, Buluk Park, Woolworths supermarket, trams and an array of great restaurants including Squires Loft, Tataki Noodles and Dumpling Restaurant and Watermark Docklands.
Please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304 to arrange an exclusive viewing

Description:
Inside and Out, the Perfect Home!
Low Rise Complex, Views to the Parkland & Etihad Stadium, Executive living, Prime position.
Feel the luxury of Docklands in this super-sized 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom apartment within walking distance of all that Melbourne has to offer. Located in the highly sought after boutique ‘Mosaic’ complex, this stunning sunlit apartment is conveniently situated among restaurants, shopping precincts, Etihad Stadium and major sporting venues, Southern Cross Station and is walking distance to Melbourne's CBD.
The building is only 9 levels high and comprises of only 70 residences. It has low body corporate fees that will appeal to owner-occupiers and perceptive investors.
The Apartment comprises of a large sized master bedroom with mirrored built in robes and ensuite, a spacious second bedroom also with a built in robe, a study, gourmet kitchen featuring stone bench tops and stainless steel (Blanco) appliances adjoining a spacious open plan living and dining area which escapes out onto an massive entertainers terrace facing to the east of Melbourne.
Also featured:
• Secure lockup car space on title
• 2 x split system heating/cooling units
• Plantation shutters
• Floorboards (carpet throughout bedrooms)
• Magnetic flyscreens
• Block-out Roller Blinds (with secured bead-chain)
• Internal security entrance
• Personal intercom
• European style laundry
• LED lighting
• Complex security cameras with personal channel
• Views of the parklands and Etihad Stadium including public transport at your doorstep.
Access to Melbourne’s leading schools and universities makes it the perfect place for students and aspiring learners;
- La Trobe University 1.4km
- Haileybury College 1.7km
- Victoria University 1.7km
- RMIT University 2.3km
- North Melbourne Primary School 3.1km
- Melbourne University 3.2km
Walking distance from DFO shopping complex, Crown Casino and Costco. Now with it's own Library, Family Community Centre, Harbour Town Shopping Centre, multiple Child-Care Centres and Primary School on the way the Docklands precinct is forming into a picture perfect place to live, and there is no wonder why so many residents are happily calling Docklands home. This is superior city-edge living with all the lifestyle benefits.
Rent back to seller an option.

Description:
Experience Bright and Stylish Docklands Living!
Central to all the amazing Docklands attractions and ideal for those who desire a light-filled and spacious apartment, this two bedroom residence in the Victoria Point complex is a stylish package ready for all buyers. With charming views including Etihad Stadium and the bay, you're moments to Docklands Park, The Hub @ Docklands, great cafes, trams, and Southern Cross Station.
Accommodation: Perfect for investors with appealing rental returns while also suited to owner-occupiers, this 20th floor property delivers open plan lounge and dining zone, stone kitchen with stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher, small balcony off the living zone which has views of the stadium, CBD buildings, and Port Phillip Bay, both bedrooms with built-in robes, well-appointed bathroom, and a European laundry
Features: Secure car space, storage cage, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, on-site building manager.
